  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Establishment of the UNIDO-BRICS Technology Exchange E-Platform</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project objective is to support the BRICS countries in their efforts to achieve technology-led development through technology transfer, as well as to stimulate partnerships thereby contributing towards the Inclusive and Sustainable Industrial Development. Implicitly, the project represents an important stepping-stone toward forging a long-term partnership between UNIDO and BRICS countries, as well as amongst the BRICS themselves in various areas related to technology exchange with the ultimate goal of expanding the e-platform to other countries.  The project outcome is the establishment of the sustainable UNIDO-BRICS Technology Exchange E-Platform, aimed at creating a database of technologies to share the best technological solutions, business models and to improve the industrial production efficiency as well as to reduce environmental footprint.  The project outcome will be achieved through establishment of the online based Technology Exchange E-Platform (Output 1) and a number of the awareness raising events in the BRICS countries and at BRICS meetings/ forums/ summits (Output 2), as well as the implementation of the Sustainability activities (Output 3). The project is divided into two phases:  1.Establishment phase (30 months), which will result into fully functional online Platform with accompanied with</narrative>
  </description>
